<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Many South African mercenaries are piloting Popular 
Movement for the Liberation of Angola-Labor Party [MPLA-PT] 
combat aircraft in Angola. Reports from the Armed Forces for 
the Liberation of Angola Military Command in Cuango area 
yesterday said the involvement of mercenaries in the MPLA-PT air 
