<F P=104>  Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The possible delay of regional voting in the 
violence-riddled kwaZulu region could be on the agenda when 
President de Klerk meets with Mr. Nelson Mandela, Dr. Mangosuthu 
