  [Text] Angola's UNITA [National Union for the Total 
Independence of Angola] movement says that up to 50 South 
African mercenaries fighting on the side of the Angolan 
Government have been killed in that country's civil war. 
UNITA's director of information in New York, Mr. (Malik Chaka), 
