  [Text] A special meeting of leaders of African states to 
discuss the political crises in Rwanda and Burundi opened in Dar 
es Salaam today. The meeting, which is being held at the 
Kilimanjaro Hotel, was opened by President Ali Hassan Mwinyi who 
