is to force the opponents of the African National Congress and 
the National Party in that region to tow the line. It all goes 
to show what kind of government we will have should the ANC ever 
be elected to rule this country. It also goes to show what type 
of rule we will have should the National Party scrape through 
with some seats in the proposed cabinet. [end recording] 

